===== Trigger =====

This class is designed to work with triggers. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:trigger:object#trigger|Trigger]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:trigger:adddependencies|trigger.adddependencies]]'' - adding new trigger dependencies
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:trigger:create|trigger.create]]'' - creating new triggers
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:trigger:delete|trigger.delete]]'' - deleting triggers
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:trigger:deletedependencies|trigger.deletedependencies]]'' - deleting trigger dependencies
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:trigger:get|trigger.get]]'' - retrieving triggers
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:trigger:update|trigger.update]]'' - updating triggers